IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. FIRSTCOBOL.
AUTHOR. HAPPY.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-NAME      PIC X(20).
01 WS-LASTNAME  PIC X(20).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
